# Steemit helper #

[![Coverage Status](https://coveralls.io/repos/github/raserrano/steemit_helper/badge.svg?branch=develop)](https://coveralls.io/github/raserrano/steemit_helper?branch=develop)

## Features ##


- [x] Voting feature
- [x] Welcome message feature
- [x] Transfer funds feature
- [x] Commenting feature
- [x] Donator transfers tracker
- [x] Poster creator
- [x] Reporter with a set of filters
- [x] Queue view, trees report view, last transactions and all transactions

